<A>__{charlie catches the clerk's attitude, but plays it cool.}
<C>__{luciano}
<D>__{mr. and mrs. charles luther.}
<C>__{registration clerk}
<P>__{(slyly taunting)}
<D>__{you wouldn't be related to the bryn mawr luthers, now would you?}
