<D>__{didn't nucky tell you about the deal with the hotel?}
<C>__{al capone}
<D>__{yeah. yeah. got me a new name, and i wore my funeral suit so they'll think i'm a fuckin' senator.}
<B>__{inside the lobby}
<A>__{capone struts up to the front desk, trailed by enough luggage to sink cleopatra's barge. impatient, capone bangs on the bell. the clerk turns around to face the counter, his eyes widening in disbelief at the vulgarity of capone's attire. he leans over the counter to take in the whole view. capone beams.}
<C>__{al capone}
<D>__{had it custom made.}
<C>__{registration clerk}
<D>__{so comforting to know there's only one.}
<A>__{capone extends a hand across the counter.}
<C>__{al capone}
<D>__{mista albert caper.}
<A>__{the clerk reluctantly shakes his hand.}
<C>__{registration clerk}
<D>__{excuse me, mr. caper.}
